title: Did Mia Khalifa "get out'Ajit Bay after" slip into her plans?
subtitle: Rumor has it that the former adult actress confronted the head of the Federal Communications Committee in Instagram after trying to send her direct flirting messages.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The President of the Federal Communications Committee, Mia Khalifa, was insulted by Ajit Bay, after sending her a letter on Instagram.
